                                                <li>Using Green's theorem, evaluate
                                                $$\int_{\partial S} \left(  3x^2 \sin{y^2} \ dx + 2x^3y \cos{y^2} \ dy  \right)$$
                                                where $S$ is any regular region with piecewise smooth boundary.</li>
                                                <br>
